Comment: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We can eat it?
Comment: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Like meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Subtitles by: /u/CatZombies\NAirdate: 2018-01-26
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get started with our first request.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.62,0:00:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Our first request is from Houtani Mizuki-san, a 25 years old office worker in Suginami Ward, Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening to everyone at the Detective Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.57,0:00:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I love pork belly stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I love, {\i1}love{\i0} that soft pork fat flavor that builds up. It's irresistible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what my request is about this time detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.18,0:00:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to eat some stew I froze in my fridge 5 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.47,0:00:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The appearance has turned pure white, so I don't know if it's edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.39,0:00:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But no matter what, I want to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, in that stew that my deceased mother made, there is her flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.63,0:00:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me make delicious, 5-year-frozen stew. Thank you very much. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.95,0:00:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was laughing at it a bit in the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but I feel like I need my handkerchief or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you may need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:01:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well still, this frozen stew is 5 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,5 years ago, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually you'd throw it away I think but,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, she wants to eat it. \NShe seems to be obsessed with the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the result? Were we able to eat that 5 year old stew? Please take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You have stew frozen from 5 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.88,0:01:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.30,0:01:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.42,0:01:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.15,0:01:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,From 5 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it'll give me stomach troubles. I want to eat it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.36,0:01:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but as you know, it's been 5 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,5 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 5 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Without Knight Scoop, you're not sure you'd be able to eat it on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.19,0:01:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.57,0:01:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well it's scary, so I thought I'd make someone do it with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.19,0:01:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, we can see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That 5 year old stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, tupperware?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tupperware.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in tupperware.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, it's ice. Inside the tupperware...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.88,0:02:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.37,0:02:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like crystals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,0:02:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this ice? This is really pretty isn't it? Isn't it intricate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In here simply put, is what you believed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not silky, right? It's all dried out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In your request letter, your mother made...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother's altar is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how she was 5 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was 20, she suddenly had a brain hemorrhage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you didn't throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That day she passed, she made stew for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.92,0:02:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:51.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,470)}The mother's final cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's why you haven't eaten it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Her last meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.73,0:03:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That morning before I went to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, my mom had work, um, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In the morning, she asked "What do you want to eat for dinner today?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I really liked stew and Mom liked stew so,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I said stew was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I said "I'm off". But when I came home,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,she had a kind of unsteady appearance so I immediately called an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I stayed at the hospital until the next morning. I didn't feel like eating or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an older sister but she's married and lives in Kumamoto Prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And my father was on a business trip in America. So I was suddenly all on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You were alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In the morning, I came back home, but
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just seeing the pot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The next day, my father came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He came back from America.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. So I put it in the tupperware.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I put it in the freezer. For some time, stew too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to eat stew for some time. It was sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason you felt like trying to eat it now is to little by little bring peace of mind to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can probably eat a little bit, I think I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be nice if you could eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I want to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to be able to eat it, but
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,on the other hand, there's the possibility that eating it is dangerous for you, Mizuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki-chan, if you got sick. Your mom wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? We can't make it. She'd be angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, we need to know if it's edible, if it's okay to eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's unsafe to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we have no choice but to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:05:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry but I don't have any days off work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you go in my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no good. It's your mom's stew. That's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,7 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, shall I investigate? Since I'm free today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I only have this, so I'm free.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, since we're researching various things about food, we've come to Tokyo University of Agriculture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Professor Uchino?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, we're from Knight Scoop. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you take a look at this for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This pork stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,For 5 years, this was frozen in the family fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? That's awfully long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,About that, can you eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I would think that after 5 years it'd be pretty difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Another thing I'd be curious about,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,how was it kept since it was prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the problem is food poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether or not any bacteria got into it before freezing is one concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,First is the microscope. To see if there are any microbes inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is bacteria, it's possible that food poisoning bacteria has gotten in as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only a little bit, but it is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There is some bacteria and it's possible it's the food poisoning type.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If we run an experiment, we can determine whether it's food poisoning bacteria or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the sudden imposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:47.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,440)}8 PM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mizuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeyama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're done?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to work like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I go to work like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, nice to meet you Dad. I'm Tantei Knight Scoop's Takeyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki, does he know the request?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times have I said "Is it okay if I throw this away?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,To your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she was strongly against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to Tokyo University of Agriculture.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done some research into whether we can eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll make a phone call and we'll hear the sensei's answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, sensei, in short, I want to ask, what's the result?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ask, I think
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,on whether or not you can eat it, you can more or less eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.31,0:07:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We can pretty much eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We can eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the microbe risk isn't zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Heat it up over 100 °C, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, if you eat a small amount,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the risk can be considerably reduced I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But it may upset your stomach a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, ok, ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it may hurt you a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't know how it will turn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.93,0:08:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important thing is that it tastes good right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We've called just the person for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayashi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.61,0:08:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop with the "good evenings".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Always calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Without warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Su-suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Making me to come to Tokyo without telling me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei's abilities are absolutely necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not bugs is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not bugs. Not bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, this is frozen stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This was frozen 5 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a small amount, it's okay to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to be able to eat this. In here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can make it from scratch of course. That 5 year old stew is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's no good. Making it from scratch is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This stew in particular, about 5 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:25.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,480)}Explaining the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last meal their mom made.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hear that, I've got to. I've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, if at all possible, I want to it as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Your mom's flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in quite a state.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The meat is awfully dried out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To restore it from being this dried out,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the broth needs to be added back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I understand, that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:09:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This smell is a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Freezer smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not confident?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for even Hayashi-sensei, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it. I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:16.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Starting cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're warming in the water to release it from the tupperware, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's come out. It's come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all in once piece because of how it came loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll not cook it too much or it'll become really dried out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow we're microwaving it to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get the feeling we'd be microwaving it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't think we'd be microwaving it to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The microwave will heat it up this way but
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,there's still the previous problem. It will become extra dry from microwaving it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll still be good even if you microwave it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:10:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The broth. The broth's come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? There's broth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's broth, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The broth's come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're separating the meat and the broth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll the use broth after I heat it up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's broth that's come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I would add some flavor but I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to heat it up to over 100 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cook it in this pressure cooker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you move them too much, they'll fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they're being cooked again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're placing them one by one so the meat doesn't lose its shape as it's heated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do it like this, it's hard for them to fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think it'd be like if sensei weren't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei is amazing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look here. There's a bit of a bad smell from the meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh huh, it's the meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Smells like meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can get rid of that bad smell a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The taste will be the same, we won't change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Spring onions and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:12:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And ginger peels. We use the peels so there's no spiciness. Only the flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,To get rid of the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not changing the mother's flavor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't change the flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't leave it in this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If we add the broth in, we can cook them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the broth you're adding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm putting it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it. I want to eat it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:31.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Has the 5 year old stew been resurrected?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch, ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no bad smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It has the perfect smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The perfect smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.71,0:12:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how your mom used to make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells just like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.49,0:12:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.49,0:12:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was this smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,While it was dried out, I tried to bring it back as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom is watching now, right? I feel like she's been brought back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we eat? As we're reminded of your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow my hands are trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Itadakimasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It tastes like your mother's cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't feel like it's been left for 5 years at all. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, are you glad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, it's really delicious after so long. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like, from tomorrow on, I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel you can?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though Dad said to throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done. Hayashi-sensei did an incredible job for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the father and Mizuki-chan had it as the mother's cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, they were able to eat the stew after being frozen for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mizuki-chan in the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,when she saw the ice crystals, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She said "This is really beautiful. I want to keep this."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She put it back in the freezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So it didn't disappear.

